*eruby-1.0.5-r2 (21 Jun 2010)

  21 Jun 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +eruby-1.0.5-r2.ebuild:
  Convert to ruby-ng.

  22 May 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  eruby-1.0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Various cleanups.

  20 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> eruby-1.0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Remove obsolete virtual/ruby dependency.

  22 Aug 2009; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> eruby-1.0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Remove ruby16 from USE_RUBY.

  13 Jun 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -eruby-1.0.5.ebuild,
  eruby-1.0.5-r1.ebuild, +files/eruby-1.0.5-missing-xldflags.patch:
  Add patch to take into account that XLDFLAGS in the ruby configuration can
  be empty. Fixes problem with configure.rb not running at all. Remove
  old version.

